{
  "stem": "25209.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I thought it was the Suez Canal but I think it must have been the war of independence in '48.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So again, we couldn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like this bloody thing, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being Jewish means you're in danger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my experience.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So-- but it was like we didn't know when this-- if they would have told that it will come in a week, in a month, in a year, you knew.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ship arrived a month later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where did it come?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why was it late one month?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you know, you're used to waiting for the train, 10 minutes long.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But one month in this, in this-- what was it called, that thing-- El Shatt, El Shatt, near, near Port Said.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so we got on this ship, and I-- Was it that same ship that was promised to you?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a little tugboat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Terrible, terrible journey-- we had-- there were some Jewish people in El Shatt that we met, a husband and wife, an old mother-- no, that was another.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were two families.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, this mother was so sick on the boat, I had to change places with her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was dying, because it was so-- it was such a bumpy ride.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we got to Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, we got to Fremantle first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's when we got to Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I looked down the ship, down the And there were all these sea of white heads and white gloves and white bags.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the women were dressed-- and I thought they were all going to a wedding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's how people used to dress in 1948, '49.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I thought they were all very strange.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
